Class AbstractLogMessageVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.caliper.bridge.AbstractLogMessageVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LogMessageVisitor

    public abstract class AbstractLogMessageVisitor
extends Object
implements LogMessageVisitor
    An abstract LogMessageVisitor with no-op implementations for the visit methods - provided so that all visitors don't have to override all methods.
